com.cloudera.cdk.data.hbase.manager
Interface ManagedSchemaDao

All Known Implementing Classes:
ManagedSchemaHBaseDao
public interface ManagedSchemaDao

Interface for fetching managed schemas from a persistence store. Managed schemas are defined by the ManagedSchema avro record. Dao implementations should be able to fetch these by key, defined by ManagedSchemaKey avro record, from the persistence store. ManagedSchemaKey is effectively a table name, entity name pair.
